{"tid":1848031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高比生前採訪：美斯似我","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:24:39.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c85859e6b4c6f027cffaeed152f268b0d70f57f","tid":1848031,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"昨天，科比和他的二女兒乘坐直升機發生事故，不幸遇難。 科比是一位足球迷，他曾多次表達自己對梅西的痴迷。 在其退役前更衣室中還貼著梅西的照片。<br />\n<br />\n 科比生前在ESPN採訪中說道：&ldquo;大家對梅西的痴迷，和對我的痴迷，我想是一樣的。我醉心於籃球，而他是足球。我們在性格上有不同，他很內向，但 對於各自領域運動的熱愛以及天賦，我們是相同的。<br />\n<br />\n ￼<br />\n<br />\n 科比遇難後，梅西在社交媒體發文沉痛悼念：&ldquo;我悲痛到說不出話，我把所有的愛都給科比的家人和朋友。很高興能與你相識，難忘那些美好時刻。一位天才 離我們而去。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9fa657c201ff763de369a64f390a9af0fe412794","tid":1848031,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=cfb2cd62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4ee74f12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&h=f2bcfe36\" data-auto-link tar